name: AppleScript Editor Plug-in
summary: Learn about .SEPLUGIN files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: SEPLUGIN files are actually bundled folders with the ".seplugin" extension. You can view their contents by removing the extension and opening the resulting folder.
Some SEPLUGIN files are included in the AppleScript Editor application bundle in the /​Contents/​Plugins/​ directory.

description: Plug-in file used by AppleScript Editor, an AppleScript program included with Mac OS X; contains functionality that extends the editor; may be a pre-installed add-on or a custom add-on created by the user.
